@startuml
title UC-03 View Course Details (Sequence)
participant User
participant WebApp
participant CourseService
participant DB
participant ReviewService
participant EnrollmentService

User -> WebApp: open course page (slug)
WebApp -> CourseService: getCourseBySlug(slug)
CourseService -> DB: SELECT course, instructor, meta
DB --> CourseService: course data
CourseService -> ReviewService: getReviews(courseId)
ReviewService -> DB: SELECT reviews
DB --> ReviewService: reviews
alt user logged in
WebApp -> EnrollmentService: checkEnrollment(userId, courseId)
EnrollmentService -> DB: SELECT enrollment
DB --> EnrollmentService: enrollmentStatus
EnrollmentService --> WebApp: status
end
CourseService --> WebApp: course + reviews + enrollmentStatus
WebApp --> User: render course page
@enduml
